tbox</a></p>\n<p><strong>Tutorial</strong>:</p>\n<p>This tutorial will show you how to open a PDF file in a lightbox using the plugin WonderPlugin Lightbox.<br />\n<span id="more-4583"></span></p>\n<p><strong>Step 1</strong>: In your WordPress post or page, create a text or image link that links to your PDF file, then in the text editor, switch to the Text mode.</p>\n<p><a href="https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/wordpress-open-pdf-in-lightbox.png" class="wplightbox"><img src="https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/wordpress-open-pdf-in-lightbox.png" alt="" width="736" height="381" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4589" srcset="https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/wordpress-open-pdf-in-lightbox.png 736w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/wordpress-open-pdf-in-lightbox-240x124.png 240w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/wordpress-open-pdf-in-lightbox-600x311.png 600w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/wordpress-open-pdf-in-lightbox-75x39.png 75w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/wordpress-open-pdf-in-lightbox-500x259.png 500w" sizes="(max-width: 736px) 100vw, 736px" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>Step 2</strong>: Add <code>class="wplightbox"</code> to the &lt;a&gt; tag.  You can also add data tag <code>data-width</code>, <code>data-height</code> to specify the maximum size of the lightbox.</p>\n<p>Here is an example:</p>\n<p><a class="wplightbox" data-width=1200 data-height=1200 href="https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/how-to-create-a-wordpress-post-carousel.pdf">Open PDF in a lightbox popup</a></p>\n<p>The code of the above example is as following:</p>\n<pre class="brush: xml; title: ; notranslate">\r\n&lt;a class=&quot;wplightbox&quot; data-width=1200 data-height=1200 href=&quot;https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/how-to-create-a-wordpress-post-carousel.pdf&quot;&gt;Open PDF in a lightbox popup&lt;/a&gt;\r\n</pre>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:39:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:3:{s:0:"";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:45:"Open a Vimeo video in a lightbox on page load";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:100:"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-video-lightbox/open-a-vimeo-video-in-a-lightbox-on-page-load/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Wed, 25 Jan 2017 01:02:32 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:18:"WordPress Lightbox";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"WordPress Lightbox Plugin";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:24:"WordPress Video Lightbox";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:36:"https://www.wonderplugin.com/?p=4562";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:400:"Product: WonderPlugin Lightbox Question: I am trying to find a wordpress plugin that will allow me to have my Vimeo video pop up in a lightbox once the home page loads - automatically. Does your plugin do this? Answer: You &#8230; <a href="https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-video-lightbox/open-a-vimeo-video-in-a-lightbox-on-page-load/">Con